.DT
event_disarm
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
event_disarm

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
event_disarm -  This function makes the more intelligent NPCs pick up their weapons after being disarmed.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void event_disarm(object disarmer,
object weapon)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^disarmer%^RESET%^ - the person who disarmed us
%^BOLD%^weapon%^RESET%^ - the weapon that was disarmed

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function makes the more intelligent NPCs pick up their
weapons after being disarmed.
It can be overwritten if you don't want the default disarm
response to work for your NPC.
.EP

